name: Enginuity Search Media
tag_list: social-search-engine, content-marketing, contextual-advertising, social-sharing, social-media, social-media-marketing, advertising, digital-marketing, brand-management
overview:
Enginuity Search Media is a company driven to help individuals, organizations and brands find socially relevant content which resonates with people.

The Enginuity search engine platform helps drive influence across multiple social networks and feeds. In addition it helps to find better product reviews that are more insightful, and highlight the popularity of content on the web.

It integrates easily with popular social media networks and dashboards like Hootsuite, Buffer, Facebook, Twitter, Pinterest and Evernote for saving and sharing content right from search pages.
